<li id="cite_note-Woods135-9"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Woods135_9-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Woods, <i>How the Church Built Western Civilization</i> (2005), p. 135</span>
